{
  "stem": "8352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The place where I come from is called-- the area was called Maramures.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was no big cities around there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Khust was one of the biggest cities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was about 30 kilometers away from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The place I come from was on the border between Romania, Poland, and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was also spoken-- Ukrainian is almost like Russian language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the house, we fluently spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The people were livin' there on agriculture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They were farming, raising potatoes, and corn, and wheat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And also a lot of lumber yard was workin' there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was a lot of lumber factories, because we had a lot of forests there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And there was also a lot of orchards there with fruit trees and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were living-- we had a little garden in the back in the back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We planted our own vegetables.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we also could rent a little piece of land and built our-- raise our own bread like wheat, and corn, and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the life going on there like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a lot of small villages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell me about your mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What-- what kinds of things did she do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what memories do you have of her?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was taking care on all the five children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was cooking all day long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was washin'.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she kept the house nice and clean and see that we are very nice, neatly dressed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a very clean lady.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was her job to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was taking care of five children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was quite a bit of work to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Full-time job.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
